graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Validating Webhook<br/>Port 9443/TCP]
        Controller -->|validates CRs| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod Architecture"
        direction TB
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>Java Service<br/>Port 8033 gRPC, 8080 internal]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Go Service<br/>Port 8001 gRPC]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>Go Service<br/>Port 8008 HTTP]
        StoragePuller[Storage Puller<br/>Go Service<br/>Port 8086 gRPC]
        ModelServer[Model Server Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe<br/>Port 8085 gRPC]

        RESTProxy -->|converts to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes requests| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|loads models| ModelServer
        ModelMesh -->|instructs download| StoragePuller
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RuntimeDeployment[Runtime Deployment<br/>2 replicas default]
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| ModelMesh

    Controller -->|creates| RuntimeService[Runtime Service<br/>ClusterIP<br/>8033 gRPC, 8008 HTTP]
    RuntimeService -->|routes to| RESTProxy
    RuntimeService -->|routes to| ModelMesh

    Controller -->|depends on| etcd[etcd<br/>Datastore<br/>Port 2379/TCP]
    ModelMesh -->|coordinates via| etcd
    StoragePuller -->|downloads from| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    Controller -->|integrates with| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management]
    Controller -->|integrates with| Monitoring[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RuntimeAdapter fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RESTProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style StoragePuller fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Monitoring fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
